Calendar
Monster Rancher Metropolis: Monster Rancher 4 Archive (PS2): FAQ: Calendar
By GoldenBoy on Saturday, December 27, 2003 - 06:06 am:

Notes:
Name- Officials are in Bold,
Tag and Group will be Italic
Location- Which arena the battle is in, important for
building Fame in that town. TAG or GRP will also be listed
here.
Item- What you win, usually food
Prize- Money for First and Second Place
Type (Opponents)- Listed as the game has them.
League battles are Round Robin where you fight everyone.
Tournament battles are elimination. Group and Tag can be of either of these types.

-Total Number of Tournaments: 128
-The main use of this calendar is for an easy reference to count ansd mark which tournaments you are missing, which is diffiult to do flipping between MR4 menus.
-A secondary use is to more easily see and mark tournaments in a given area, if you feel the need to increase fame in a certain spot. This on matters with Torble, as far as we know, but it can't hurt to have 100 fame across the whole world!
